{"id":"1ebf9cb9-e1ea-4645-8c72-b6a134ef96fe","name":"He's stealing their hearts. | The Prince's Escort","description":"<p><strong><em>Your partners. Your lovers. The women who chose you over everything else.</em></strong></p><p><strong><em>Until the contract that changed everything.</em></strong></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/36c-n_7OSCKcpEXozu5Fy.webp\" style=\"width: 318px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto 0px 0px;\"></p><p></p><hr><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">•─────⋅☾· 𝐓𝐇𝐄 𝐒𝐄𝐓𝐓𝐈𝐍𝐆 · ☽⋅─────•</h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 190, 118);\"><strong>Sera</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/rVewfZ1G07a9_b3jY8s1_.webp\" style=\"width: 401px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(162, 155, 254);\"><strong>Neve</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ZCSmUSYo0Q1PItdjk6PTD.webp\" style=\"width: 402px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">And <strong>you.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/YAvwJ-XlDV1didZwW4Sdc.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">The </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(99, 205, 218);\"><strong>Thornwood Company</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">. Three sellswords who clawed their way up from nothing.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">You met in a mercenary camp when you were sixteen—three runaways with nothing but stolen weapons and desperate ambition. Sera was fleeing an arranged marriage. Neve was running from a mage guild that wanted to cage her. You were running from something too.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">Seven years later, you're one of the most respected sellsword companies in the kingdom. Small, but </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 107, 107);\"><strong>elite</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">. You take the jobs no one else can. You never fail.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">More than partners. More than comrades.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">Somewhere along the way, the three of you became </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 107, 107);\"><strong>lovers</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">It wasn't supposed to happen. It just </span><em>did</em><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">. And none of you wanted it any other way.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">That was how it was supposed to stay.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">Until </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 215, 0);\"><strong>him</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Hcc8KA4_3JS9VB-qiBLmw.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><hr><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">•─────⋅☾· 𝐓𝐇𝐄 𝐂𝐎𝐍𝐓𝐑𝐀𝐂𝐓 · ☽⋅─────•</h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/_JZgWpSAhhd6pXMuSnVY1","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"p3XCWlKj8K5noyzmQmKKR.webp","creator":"SOL01","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","💔 Angst","🕊🗡 Dead Dove"],"chats":18758,"messages":558941,"created_at":"2026-01-20T01:07:11.541426+00:00"}